org.drip.param.market
Class BasketMarketParams

java.lang.Object
  org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      org.drip.param.market.BasketMarketParams

public class BasketMarketParams
extends Serializer

This class provides an implementation of BaketMarketParamsRef for a specific scenario. Contains maps holding named discount curves, named credit curves, named treasury quote, named component quote, and fixings object.
